1.0.0
    Initial convey.
    This work is based on Reloadr (https://github.com/hoh/reloadr).
    Made some functions to be public to suppress IDE's warning.
    Added ways to stop periodical reloads and to stop reloads on file modifications.
    Added decorators for periodical reloading.
    Added decorators to set an event handler instance that handles a callback on reload
        and to set a file path to be observed for reloading the target.
    Added logging.
